The /stalking idea has been brought up before and had much support. Again, this would be for PCs only with a limited range.<br>
<br>
For PvE it would indeed be more of a &quot;toy&quot; or &quot;bone&quot; as someone mentioned, perhaps nothing more than a roleplay tool and a nice way to be able to find your friends as you come to join them in a group.<br>
<br>
I championed a Stalking ability mainly for PvP rogues. It would be some recompense for the taking away of egg shaped pumice and for the blow to poisons felt long ago. <p><img src="http://www.thesafehouse.org/%7Efricka/sig/DAOCsig.jpg"><br><b>~Fricka</b>
