Bards get Track because - in EQ at least - they are the &quot;Jack of all trades, Master of none&quot;.<br>
<br>
Skills we get that make little sense for &quot;musicians&quot; to have (but perfect sense for the Jack):<br>
<br>
1. Track - Ranger<br>
2. Hide - Rogue/Ranger<br>
3. Sneak - Rogue/Ranger/Monk<br>
4. Safe Fall - Rogue/Monk<br>
5. Instill Doubt - Rogue/Monk<br>
6. Forage - Ranger<br>
7. Pick Lock - Rogue<br>
8. Sense Trap - Rogue<br>
9. Disarm Trap - Rogue<br>
